{"tid":1552764,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請各位香港人以被警捉到就等同\"死亡\"為前題行事","createTime":"2019-09-08T11:54:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T07:54:39.000Z","uid":263448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9820f8d208d063b600ec64fb07024db75a7070ca","tid":1552764,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:54:14.000Z","msg":"係到，我唔會再分藍黃、中立、和理非、勇武。<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">因為&quot;病毒&quot;唔分人種、膚色、政治立場。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港一日未贏，我地一日都有無數既香港人&quot;死亡&quot;。<br />\n一停落黎，&quot;病毒&quot;就會擴散，所以香港人要抵抗</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">最近有不少離奇死亡，一啲無權無勢，朋友少，親戚少既人，「抗體差」既香港人，必死無疑。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而且&quot;病毒&quot;，已經唔比香港人&quot;說出名字&quot;</span>，點救？<br />\n<strong>當&quot;病毒&quot;入侵咗香港人體內，查證佢全家有咩人，&quot;容易處理&quot;既人，必然死於非命，你估真係48小時後無事？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n寫定<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「不自殺聲明」</span></strong>係必須的，但呢啲只係保險，因為你死咗，已經無用。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">短期</span>要解決既話，就必須全民帶武，群起反抗，但香港人好和善、怕死，明明警方都&quot;指虛烏有話驚搶犯&quot;，點解無人真係搶犯？<br />\n因為<span style=\"color: gold;\">大家都無&quot;互信&quot;</span>，你郁手，其他人唔郁，只係送頭。<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">你企係到，&quot;病毒&quot;係咪都入侵你，因為你係香港人</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">你反抗，起碼都可以跑贏佢地</span>。<span style=\"color: gold;\">一車人反抗，大家都安全</span>。<br />\n<br />\n長遠要根治，相信大家都明要點根治，就唔多講了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，想知道真相，想平亂，就只能贏。</span></strong></span><br />\n政府無能，警察暴動。<br />\n香港人只能被迫成立新政府，取代舊政府。<br />\n國際救援刻不容緩。"},{"pid":"289f47ccd6317999d4d0acb521dc3fc35d33b11b","tid":1552764,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8772a15760b33d1043fa357c98e43d907e802e","tid":1552764,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c2dbfa2ea2200d37071481b750950bd53930da","tid":1552764,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}